The effective protection of the EU’s external borders is crucial to ensure internal security. 
We want to strengthen the European Border and Coast Guard Agency with a new standing corps of around 10,000 #EUBorderGuard. 
Learn more → https://t.co/AeLJNLMFTb https://t.co/oZIicN1iDt

We propose to allocate €21.3 billion to border management overall and create a new Integrated Border Management Fund worth more than €9.3 billion. This will better protect the EU's external borders together with a stronger #EUBorderGuard → https://t.co/AeLJNLMFTb https://t.co/3XZllnp0YM

Our new Asylum and Migration Fund will focus on: 
⚙️ A stronger and more efficient European asylum system
📄 Greater support for legal migration and integration
⏲️ Faster and more frequent returns
Learn more → https://t.co/AeLJNLMFTb #MigrationEU https://t.co/ojLNpElsE7

In our long term #EUBudget, we want to increase funding for Asylum and Migration Fund by 51%. It will support EU countries' efforts in: 
✅Asylum
